    "slug": "a-black-woman-making-art-is-a-disruptive-act-every-story-that-i-tell-as-a-woman",
    "texto": "A black woman making art is a disruptive act. Every story that I tell as a woman is a political act, even if I want to tell a 'silly love story.' The fact it exists through my gaze is radical.",
